        __description4: "<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left\"><ul><li><span>There is no restriction on how to leave a vehicle standing in a roadway. </span></li><li><span id=\"correctAnswer0221\">Parallel to the road’s edge or according to the road’s marking.</span></li><li><span>Perpendicularly to the road’s edge. </span></li><li><span>In an angle of no more than thirty degrees from the kerb.</span></li></ul><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: right;padding-top: 4px;\"><span>| «C1» | «C» | «D» | «1» | «В» | </span><span style=\"float: left;\"><button type=\"button\" onclick=\"var correctAnswer=document.getElementById('correctAnswer0221');correctAnswer.style.background='yellow'\">Correct Answer</button></span></div></div>",
